title: Radioheads 'The Trends' 4/27: Famotidine, Memorial Day 2020, Kristin Cavallari, Dennis Rodman
itunes:title: Radioheads 'The Trends' 4/27: Famotidine, Memorial Day 2020, Kristin Cavallari, Dennis Rodman
description:
On this edition of Radiohead's 'The Trends' Jack and Miles discuss the active ingredient in Pepcid being the next supposed miracle cure for COVID, Pence says we'll be past the worst of it by Memorial Day weekend, Kirstin Cavallari and Jay Cutler have decided to split after 10 years of marriage, and Bill Simmons has come under fire for suggesting that Dennis Rodman is not interesting.
